        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran's top diplomat says a lack of trust is impeding talks to end war with the US</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Iran’s foreign minister says that a lack of trust remains the biggest obstacle in negotiations to end the war with the U.S. Iranian Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi said contradictory messages from the U.S. have made Iran reluctant about its intentions in the stalled ceasefire negotiations.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/15/irans-top-diplomat-says-a-lack-of-trust-is-impeding-talks-to-end-war-with-the-us/"  >(Sheikh Saaliq And Adam Schreck, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 15 May 2026 18:04:26 GMT">
