        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump administration prepares to seek Ra&#250;l Castro indictment as it pressures Cuba, AP sources say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Justice Department is preparing to seek an indictment against former Cuban President Raúl Castro, three people familiar with the matter tell The Associated Press.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/15/us-eyes-indictment-against-raul-castro-amid-pressure-by-trump-administration-sources-tell-ap/"  >(Joshua Goodman, Alanna Durkin Richer And Eric Tucker, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
