        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Woman who spent 7 years in Chinese prison describes torture, surveillance and loss of her husband</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Wang Chunyan claims the the CCP destroyed her family, imprisoned her for seven years and killed her husband in its campaign against Falun Gong practitioners.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/10/woman-who-spent-7-years-chinese-prison-describes-torture-surveillance-loss-her-husband/"  >(Fox News)</a>
