      <img src="/static14/tech/2026/05/13/saps-ai-promises-last-year-most-are-still-rolling-out-2.webp" alt="SAP&#8217;s AI promises last year? Most are still rolling out" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">SAP&#8217;s AI promises last year? Most are still rolling out</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAP made bold promises about AI at Sapphire 2025: Knowledge Graph, Joule Studio, and AI Agent Hub would ship by the end of the year. Those tools are now technically available, but adoption has lagged, and SAP is already announcing version 2.0.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/13/saps-ai-promises-last-year-most-are-still-rolling-out-2/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 15 May 2026 07:00:00 GMT">
