        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The trouble with emotion-reading AI</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      “If you can’t measure it, you can’t fix it.” 
That’s a common saying in business, and it tends to be true. But what if the thing you want to fix is your employees’ attitudes? 
The AI revolution makes it possible to measure emotions and mental states.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/15/the-trouble-with-emotion-reading-ai/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
