        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hard drive shortages are putting the squeeze on enterprise storage buyers</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      It is no secret that there is a considerable shortage of storage devices, both traditional spinning media and SSDs. It’s always been hard to quantify beyond the “they are out of stock” complaints, but now some companies are sharing tangible stats.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/13/hard-drive-shortage-affecting-enterprise-storage-needs/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
