    <h3 itemprop="headline">Navy veteran Rocky Rochford seeks to turn Tampa Bay red, unseat 20-year House incumbent</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Retired Commodore Rocky Rochford pledges to be ready to lead on day one, with legislation ready to introduce into Congress.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/15/navy-veteran-rocky-rochford-seeks-turn-tampa-bay-red-unseat-20-year-house-incumbent/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
